description: Returns the IAM roles that are associated with the specified ACM (ACM) certificate. It also returns the name of the Amazon S3 bucket and the Amazon S3 object key where the certificate, certificate chain, and encrypted private key bundle are stored, and the ARN of the KMS key that's used to encrypt the private key.

parameters.name: CertificateArn
parameters.description: The ARN of the ACM certificate for which to view the associated IAM roles, encryption keys, and Amazon S3 object information.

nested_items.name: AssociatedRoles
nested_items.description: Information about the associated IAM roles.

nested_items.name: AssociatedRoleArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the associated IAM role.

nested_items.name: CertificateS3BucketName
nested_items.description: The name of the Amazon S3 bucket in which the Amazon S3 object is stored.

nested_items.name: CertificateS3ObjectKey
nested_items.description: The key of the Amazon S3 object where the certificate, certificate chain, and encrypted private key bundle are stored. The object key is formatted as follows: role_arn/ certificate_arn.

nested_items.name: EncryptionKmsKeyId
nested_items.description: The ID of the KMS key used to encrypt the private key.
